TFRRS Profile

2024 Outdoor Track: Placed second in the pole vault with a clearance of 15-9 3/4 at the Badger Challenge (May 3)...finished 15th in the pole vault with a clearance of 16-4 3/4 at the Battle on the Bayou (March 29)...set a personal best in the pole vault, finishing third with a clearance of 16-11 at the Keyth Talley Invitational (March 23)

2024 Indoor Track: Set a personal best and finished seventh in the pole vault with a clearance of 16-10 at the Big Ten Championships...placed fourth in the pole vault with a clearance of 16-03 1/4 at the Windy City Invitational (Feb. 9)...finished third in the pole vault with a jump of 16-4 3/4 at the Larry Wieczorek Invitational (Jan. 19)...finished second in the pole vault with a clearance of 16-7 1/2 at the Wisconsin Midwest Invitational (Jan. 13)

2023 Outdoor Track: Placed ninth in the pole vault with a clearance of 15-10 1/2 at the Big Ten Outdoor Championships (May 12-14)...won the pole vault with a jump of 16-4 3/4 at the Wisconsin Classic (May.5)

2023 Indoor Track: Placed second in the pole vault with a clearance of 15-6 1/4 at the Badgers Valentines Day Invite (Feb.17)...finished fourth in the pole vault with a clearance of 15-4 1/2 at the Windy City Invite (Feb.10-11)...won the pole vault with a clearance of 15-7 at the Illini Challenge (Jan.27-28)...finished second and threw a personal best of 15-9 in the men's pole vault at the Larry Wieczorek Invite (Jan.20-21)

2022 Outdoor Track: Redshirt season ... competed unattached and finished fifth in the pole vault at the Wisconsin Classic (May 6) with a personal best of 15-5 1/2

2022 Indoor Track: Placed sixth in the pole vault with a clearance of 14-6 1/4 at the Badgers' St. Valentines Open (Feb.18) ... finished ninth in the pole vault with a clearance of 15-1 at the Badgers Windy City Invitational (Feb. 11) ... came in ninth in the pole vault with a personal best clearance of 15-5 at the Indiana Relays (Jan.28)

High School: Won the pole vault at the 2021 Texas Elite Pole Vault Expo Explosion ... played 14th in the vault at the 2021 Adidas Indoor nationals ... won the pole vault at the 2020 USATF Indoor Championship ... took third in the 2020 AAU National Pole Vault Invitational

Personal: Born Feb. 1 ... major is engineering mechanics
